{"sn1.25:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.25 ","sn1.25:0.2":"3. Sattivagga ","sn1.25:0.3":"Arahantasutta ","sn1.25:1.1":"“Yo hoti bhikkhu araham katavi, ","sn1.25:1.2":"Khinasavo antimadehadhari; ","sn1.25:1.3":"Aham vadamitipi so vadeyya, ","sn1.25:1.4":"Mamam vadantitipi so vadeyya”ti. ","sn1.25:2.1":"“Yo hoti bhikkhu araham katavi, ","sn1.25:2.2":"Khinasavo antimadehadhari; ","sn1.25:2.3":"Aham vadamitipi so vadeyya, ","sn1.25:2.4":"Mamam vadantitipi so vadeyya; ","sn1.25:2.5":"Loke samannam kusalo viditva, ","sn1.25:2.6":"Voharamattena so vohareyya”ti. ","sn1.25:3.1":"“Yo hoti bhikkhu araham katavi, ","sn1.25:3.2":"Khinasavo antimadehadhari; ","sn1.25:3.3":"Manam nu kho so upagamma bhikkhu, ","sn1.25:3.4":"Aham vadamitipi so vadeyya; ","sn1.25:3.5":"Mamam vadantitipi so vadeyya”ti. ","sn1.25:4.1":"“Pahinamanassa na santi gantha, ","sn1.25:4.2":"Vidhupita managanthassa sabbe; ","sn1.25:4.3":"Sa vitivatto mannatam sumedho, ","sn1.25:4.4":"Aham vadamitipi so vadeyya. ","sn1.25:5.1":"Mamam vadantitipi so vadeyya, ","sn1.25:5.2":"Loke samannam kusalo viditva; ","sn1.25:5.3":"Voharamattena so vohareyya”ti. "}